description: The Science Fair is an annual event where students showcase their scientific experiments and innovations.
Our talented spellers compete in the Spelling Bee to demonstrate their vocabulary skills.
Cultural Diversity Day celebrates our multicultural community with music, food, and traditional performances.
The Mathematics Olympiad is a challenging competition that tests the mathematical skills of our students.
The Drama Club's performance promises an evening of theatrical excellence and storytelling.
Students engage in spirited debates on important topics during our annual Debate Tournament.
The Art and Craft Workshop provides students with hands-on creative experiences and artistic expression.
The Career Guidance Seminar helps students explore career options and make informed decisions about their future.
Our Sports Day is a day of friendly competition, promoting physical fitness and teamwork among students.
The Music Recital showcases the musical talents of our students with captivating performances.
The Robotics Workshop allows students to explore the world of robotics and engineering through hands-on activities.
The Annual Talent Show is a showcase of the diverse talents and skills of our students.
